POST http://localhost:8080/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

> {% client.global.set("customerId", response.body.id) %}

### Create Source Account (Checking)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "{{customerId}}",
  "currency": "USD",
  "accountType": "CHECKING",
  "initialBalance": 1000.00
}

> {% client.global.set("sourceAccountId", response.body.id) %}

### Create Destination Account (Savings)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "{{customerId}}",
  "currency": "USD",
  "accountType": "SAVINGS",
  "initialBalance": 50.00
}

> {% client.global.set("destAccountId", response.body.id) %}

### Make Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceAccountId": "{{sourceAccountId}}",
  "destinationAccountId": "{{destAccountId}}",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Check Source Account Balance (Should be $900)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/{{sourceAccountId}}

### Check Destination Account Balance (Should be $150)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/{{destAccountId}}
